Theresa L. QUINN, Individually and as Administratrix of the Estate of Robert J. Quinn, Deceased, Appellant, v. Motorship THE KUNGSHOLM, Her Engines, etc., and A/B Svenska Amerika Linien, Appellee. No. 350. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. June 13, 1938. Horace M. Gray, of New York City, 'for appellant. John W. Griffin, of New York City, for appellee.

• Before L. HAND, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed on opinion below.
